The director of a jail for juvenile gang members was gunned down in the streets to work on Friday .
Luis Andres Cuyun , 30 , was riding in a car when two suspected Mara Salvatrucha members opened fired on him and his driver , injured in the attack .
A Salvadoran Juan Carlos Medina Luna , 29 , and Guatemalan Mario Alfonso Aguilar , 18 , were arrested after a police chase .